name: Fill the contact form and send it
description: As a user I should be able to fill the contact form and send it

steps.name: the user navigates to the home page
click on the contact link on the bottom of the page
fill the fields 'Hi, how are you?', 'Zeus Lopes' and 'test@mail.com.br'
click on the radio box to confirm the sharing
the user needs to see the 'Message Sent Successfully!'

name: Navigate to a destination through the menu on the top left
description: As a user I can Navigate to a destination using the menu located on the top left of the page

elements.name: Navigate to a destination with success

steps.name: the user navigates to the home page
click on the menu on the top-left of the page
select the first destination of the list
the user should see the appropriate destination page

name: Subscribe to the Newsletter
description: As a user I can Subscribe the Newsletter

steps.name: the user navigates to the home page
click on the button to Subscribe the newsletter
the user sees a 'You are now checked-in!'
the user navigates to the home page
fill the field email with a 'invalid_email.com'
click on the button to Subscribe the newsletter
the user sees a error message: 'Please enter a valid e-mail address'
